By":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:07:08.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n人地CEO都出哂口術啦<br />\n<br />\n國泰:員工支持或參與非法示威將受處分<br />\n<br />\n國泰航空(00293)行政總裁何杲在一封給員工的信中表示，集團對不合法活動「零容忍」，如果員工支持或參與非法示威，將會接受紀律處分，其中可能包括終止僱用。<br />\n<br />\n何杲在信中提到，最近有員工向外披露公司機密資料，有違行為守則，情況完全不能接受。他提醒員工，即使在工餘時間，他們的行為及言論會對公司造成重大影響；他又稱，公司的社交媒體守則明確指出員工不可發布任何侵犯同事私隱、構成欺凌，以及令國泰蒙羞的言論。<br />\n<br />\n何杲指出，今日在機場舉行的示威並未得到官方批准，所以會被視為非法示威，重申國泰員工切勿支持或參與相關示威。<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2217487/%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0:%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%88%96%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E5%B0%87%E5%8F%97%E8%99%95%E5%88%86?fbclid=IwAR2CrXe8g5CIhCWF94NtUE-5KTl5-iFvHsHaUGuxjIbbTzT0hhRaVatl3kM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2217487%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%25B0%3A%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%2588%2586%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2CrXe8g5CIhCWF94NtUE-5KTl5-iFvHsHaUGuxjIbbTzT0hhRaVatl3kM&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ6npKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=3b91464d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2217487/%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0:%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E6%88%96%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E5%B0%87%E5%8F%97%E8%99%95%E5%88%86?fbclid=IwAR2CrXe8g5CIhCWF94NtUE-5KTl5-iFvHsHaUGuxjIbbTzT0hhRaVatl3kM</a>"},{"pid":"390d6bceedddf31dbc68b5bf996550d62288ec75","tid":1454320,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eace959368c00274568eca0061c3a6cd30f0e5e4","tid":1454320,"uid":54791,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:06:30.000Z","msg":"國泰就算跪低我都會支持<br />\n冇佢地一早冇人罷工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:07:42.000Z","msg":"嗰個係國泰工會, 唔係公司"},{"pid":"183e5bad0cd38f2ce69cdeda03d9001acff0b11a","tid":1454320,"uid":